{"id": 225025376, "title": "Former Boston teacher allegedly sent explicit texts to teen, possessed child porn", "text": "A former Boston teacher from Quincy was arrested last week for allegedly possessing child porngraphy, federal prosecutors said. Carter Peaseley, 40, was arrested on Thursday and is charged with possession and receipt of child pornography, the U.S. Attorney\u2019s Office said. According to court documents, investigators found 243 images of child sexual abuse materials on his computer and cellphone. He was also allegedly in an online relationship with a 15-year-old, which included the exchange of explicit photographs. Peaseley had previously worked at the John D. O\u2019Bryant School of Mathematics and Science and the Match Charter School in Boston, prosecutors said. The O\u2019Bryant School in Roxbury is a Boston Public Schools high school. Peaseley\u2019s online relationship with the 15-year-old lasted for about a year, federal prosecutors allege. He allegedly told the child to delete their texts and suggested using a different platform. Federal prosecutors said Peaseley and the child exchanged photographs, including sexually explicit photos of the child. He also allegedly said he wanted to teach the child \u201chow to kiss, among other sexually explicit activities,\u201d and discussed planning to visit in person. Peaseley is facing a minimum of five and up to 20 years in prison, up to a lifetime of supervised release, and a fine of $250,000.", "summary": "<p>Peaseley previously worked at the John D. O\u2019Bryant School of Mathematics and Science and the Match Charter School in Boston.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.boston.com/news/local-news/2024/05/28/former-boston-teacher-allegedly-sent-explicit-texts-to-teen-possessed-child-porn/\">Former Boston teacher allegedly sent explicit texts to teen, possessed child porn</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.boston.com\">Boston.com</a>.</p>", "url": "https://www.boston.com/news/local-news/2024/05/28/former-boston-teacher-allegedly-sent-explicit-texts-to-teen-possessed-child-porn/", "image": "https://bdc2020.o0bc.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/BDC_Logo_2020_256x256-60d0abc34135e.png", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 13:11:08", "author": "Molly Farrar", "authors": ["Molly Farrar"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": -0.081}